UPJS is a javascript library that caters for the needs and requirements of web developers. 
UPJS can be categorized into two, which are its core functions and its extensions like 
cookie.js and validator.js. Core library supports basic functionalities of the library
and extensions are to provide additional improvements on the library. From an architectural
perspective, UPJS aims 3 layer approach. First layer is UPJS core functionalities, second
for its extensions and last layer for its plugins.

